&GLOBAL
  PROGRAM_NAME ATOM
&END GLOBAL
&ATOM
  ELEMENT Ba 

  RUN_TYPE PSEUDOPOTENTIAL_OPTIMIZATION

  ELECTRON_CONFIGURATION  [Xe] 6s2
  CORE [Xe] 
  MAX_ANGULAR_MOMENTUM 2

  &METHOD
     METHOD_TYPE  KOHN-SHAM
     RELATIVISTIC DKH(3)
     &XC
       &XC_FUNCTIONAL PBE0
       &END XC_FUNCTIONAL
     &END XC
  &END METHOD
  &OPTIMIZATION
