                       0.39891644414787
    0.86063234330597       1   -0.83424045283420
    &END 
    CONFINEMENT_TYPE  BARRIER
    CONFINEMENT 200. 4.0 12.0 
  &END POTENTIAL

  &POWELL
     ACCURACY   1.e-14
     STEP_SIZE  0.001
     STEP_SIZE_SCALING  0.90
     MAX_INIT   50
     MAX_FUN    50
     WEIGHT_PSIR0 0.0
